  "title": "Customer Service Executive (5 days / East / Freight Forwarding)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Assist the Customer Service Department, reporting to the Team Manager.</li>\n  <li>Self-driven and capable of working independently.</li>\n  <li>Open to learning and taking on new responsibilities.</li>\n  <li>Basic understanding of air and sea logistics is a plus.</li>\n  <li>Oversee air and sea shipment bookings efficiently.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with air and sea carriers to ensure smooth operations.</li>\n  <li>Maintain clear and professional communication with customers.</li>\n  <li>Manage sea freight documentation, including bookings and bills of lading.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No. 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
